<td colspan=2><div class=title>Systematic Versus Stochastic Constraint Satisfaction</div>
<tt>Eugene C. Freuder (<A href="mailto:ecf@cs.unh.edu">ecf@cs.unh.edu</A>), 
Rina Dechter (<A href="mailto:dechter@ics.uci.edu">dechter@ics.uci.edu</A>),
Matthew L. Ginsberg (<A href="mailto:ginsberg@cs.uoregon.edu">ginsberg@cs.uoregon.edu</A>),
Bart Selman (<A href="mailto:selman@research.att.com">selman@research.att.com</A>) &
Edward Tsang   (<A href="mailto:edward@essex.ac.uk">edward@essex.ac.uk</A>)
</tt></td></tr>
